<paragraph id="71A49BDEF0D339BC44BAD6194C4CCEC7" pageId="0" pageNumber="101">CHINA: Holotype â™‚, Manghe Macaques National Nature Reserve, Yangcheng County, Shanxi Province, 3.viii.2013, coll. Shulian Hao and Yanjun Fan (gen. slide no. L14058) (NKU).</paragraph>
