<paragraph id="DE25FDF231EF5D8F3DF6EE8C4A0BD0CE" pageId="0" pageNumber="101">China (Shanxi).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C8077CFB6D7521B05F120C5B0849A002" pageId="0" pageNumber="101" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="3EB327F5C815543F80113BA5364E9925" pageId="0" pageNumber="101">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F68F84190DE9DFAD9BC91B986689EA35" pageId="0" pageNumber="101">
This new species is named in honour of the late Professor Youqiao Liu (Beijing, China), who was a famous expert of 
<taxonomicName id="9A813A2FEBF9E1DBA83CFA62BCD84740" lsidName="" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="101" rank="order">Lepidoptera</taxonomicName>
in China.
</paragraph>
